=Description=

The project is named ESSglobal. The ESSglobal working group meets regularly, and the project was also presented at the FIESS2011 in Montreal, Canada. 

You will find here the ESSglobal report of FIESS2011:

Report ESSglobal FIESS2011 (in English): http://www.ripesseu.net/fileadmin/ripessEU.net/files/files/ESSglobal/ESSGlobal_memo_fiess2011_eng.pdf


